#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dropna.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dropna"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:1 of
msgid "Remove missing values."
msgstr "移除缺失值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:3 of
msgid ""
"See the :ref:`User Guide <missing_data>` for more on which values are "
"considered missing, and how to work with missing data."
msgstr ""
"参见 :ref:`用户指南 <missing_data>` 了解更多关于哪些值被视为缺失以及如何"
"处理缺失数据的信息。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:6 of
msgid ""
"Determine if rows or columns which contain missing values are removed.  *"
" 0, or 'index' : Drop rows which contain missing values. * 1, or "
"'columns' : Drop columns which contain missing value."
msgstr ""
"确定是否移除包含缺失值的行或列。  * 0 或 'index'：删除包含缺失值的行。 * "
"1 或 'columns'：删除包含缺失值的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:6 of
msgid "Determine if rows or columns which contain missing values are removed."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:9 of
msgid "0, or 'index' : Drop rows which contain missing values."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:10 of
msgid "1, or 'columns' : Drop columns which contain missing value."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:12 of
msgid ""
"Determine if row or column is removed from DataFrame, when we have at "
"least one NA or all NA.  * 'any' : If any NA values are present, drop "
"that row or column. * 'all' : If all values are NA, drop that row or "
"column."
msgstr ""
"确定在至少有一个 NA 或全部为 NA 时是否从 DataFrame 中删除行或列。  * 'any"
"'：如果存在任何 NA 值，则删除该行或列。 * 'all'：如果所有值都是 NA，则"
"删除该行或列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:12 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Determine if row or column is removed from DataFrame, when we have at "
"least one NA or all NA."
msgstr ""
"确定在至少有一个 NA 或全部为 NA 时是否从 DataFrame 中删除行或列。  * 'any"
"'：如果存在任何 NA 值，则删除该行或列。 * 'all'：如果所有值都是 NA，则"
"删除该行或列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:15 of
msgid "'any' : If any NA values are present, drop that row or column."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:16 of
msgid "'all' : If all values are NA, drop that row or column."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:18 of
msgid "Require that many non-NA values."
msgstr "要求有这么多非 NA 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:20 of
msgid ""
"Labels along other axis to consider, e.g. if you are dropping rows these "
"would be a list of columns to include."
msgstr ""
"要考虑的其他轴上的标签，例如，如果您正在删除行，则这些将是需要包含的列"
"列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:23 of
msgid "If True, do operation inplace and return None."
msgstr "如果为 True，则就地执行操作并返回 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:25 of
msgid "If True, the resulting axis will be labeled 0, 1, …, n - 1."
msgstr "如果为 True，则结果轴将被标记为 0, 1, …, n - 1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.dropna.df_dropna:28 of
msgid "DataFrame with NA entries dropped from it."
msgstr "从中删除了 NA 条目的 DataFrame。"

